a8f7949b-3594-488c-9195-16abc0cdb82b.title: <player>
a8f7949b-3594-488c-9195-16abc0cdb82b.text: What would happen if I were to say...

d84bcca0-94ef-4c77-a3b5-774081133d80.title: 'The Guns'
d84bcca0-94ef-4c77-a3b5-774081133d80.text: Stop! Stop! Humpf...I'll beat you to...urghh...a pulp!

144dcd45-d4e0-45b2-bc59-e8872e162a89.title: <player>
144dcd45-d4e0-45b2-bc59-e8872e162a89.text:
Hi, I'm looking to get some kit to look like one of you
guys. Anything you might be able to help me out with?

c22c6532-595b-4af3-b918-760d05de29d5.title: 'The Guns'
c22c6532-595b-4af3-b918-760d05de29d5.text: Well... Urmpf! Ye can 'ave me shirt...

eb085481-2197-45d6-a37f-60893849047b.title: <player>
eb085481-2197-45d6-a37f-60893849047b.text:
Hmmm. Has it been cleaned? I don't want some sweaty
hand-me-down.

65a2b224-25c5-455f-8836-0bb7b5596e3e.title: 'The Guns'
65a2b224-25c5-455f-8836-0bb7b5596e3e.text: What? Huhmf! It ain't ever been...uurrgg...worn.

b8c3e502-8d07-4b83-864c-b15cca6b204d.title: <player>
b8c3e502-8d07-4b83-864c-b15cca6b204d.text: Well, that sounds good. Can I have it then?

917bc1c9-5873-41d0-9707-66fdef6f81bf.title: 'The Guns'
917bc1c9-5873-41d0-9707-66fdef6f81bf.text:
Can't...hurrr...see why not. This is firsty work doh.
Could do wiv a beer.

b891882c-4d7c-4f79-87ed-e183b9867918.title: 'The Guns'
b891882c-4d7c-4f79-87ed-e183b9867918.text:
I'm a simple...umph...man. I like the bar in Yanille and
their cheap beer...

02e49206-6263-422e-944c-6c325b400441.title: <player>
02e49206-6263-422e-944c-6c325b400441.text:
What do you do when you're not lifting logs above
your head?

f243cca0-17cf-4984-8609-9ee2bedaa42a.title: 'The Guns'
f243cca0-17cf-4984-8609-9ee2bedaa42a.text:
All sorts. I like...hummff...a good kebab and a cold beer
down...urrghh...the pub. And for those quiet
evenings...hurrr...

d8d61ffe-f687-470a-ba91-737d0a3516c6.title: 'The Guns'
d8d61ffe-f687-470a-ba91-737d0a3516c6.text: A bit of needlepoint is always welcome.

cc3fa62c-5963-4619-bc50-b7eae4fc7f1f.title: <player>
cc3fa62c-5963-4619-bc50-b7eae4fc7f1f.text: I can honestly say you're a very original guy.
